{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"0602b4e389f54f3efff2f30f90bb01d0","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the submit API to also trigger the AI generation after creating the task. Actually, I should make this a separate step so the admin can review before sending to AI, or we can auto-trigger. Let me check the current submit flow - it looks like it just creates the task with \"pending\" status.\n\nActually, looking at the workflow in the plan, the flow should be:\n1. Client submits product (status: submitted)\n2. Admin reviews and approves (moves to queued)\n3. AI generates images\n4. Admin reviews generated images (moves to reviewing)\n5. Client sees and confirms\n\nBut wait, looking at the Phase 3 completion and the current submit flow, it seems like submission immediately creates an AI task. Let me reconsider the workflow based on the spec.\n\nLooking at productStatusEnum:\n- draft → submitted → queued → processing → reviewing → client_reviewing → feedback_received → reworking → completed → failed → cancelled\n\nThe flow seems to be:\n1. draft: User creates product\n2. submitted: User submits, credits frozen, AI task created (pending)\n3. queued: Admin approves, moves to queue for AI\n4. processing: AI is generating\n5. reviewing: AI done, admin reviewing\n6. client_reviewing: Ready for client to see\n7. completed: Client confirmed\n\nBut I've already modified the submit API to create a task with \"pending\" status. Let me also add an admin endpoint to approve and trigger AI generation, so the admin has control.\n\nActually, let me simplify: the current submit API creates a task with \"pending\" status. I'll also need to add a way to trigger the AI. Let me update the admin products API to allow approving and triggering AI.\n\nActually, let me also create a simple admin API to trigger AI for pending tasks. But first, let me check if the project builds.","signature":"94a54c79d3cf8b27b8814ca72bbf90e3329fbf42c86649a590ad0e5da6333e51"}],"model":"MiniMax-M2.5","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":146,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1348,"cache_read_input_tokens":38573},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0fe3e04a-e649-4c3b-ad04-3a2fa78bad13","uuid":"a4b006d5-a1f5-49f7-965b-c3c82012f8b9"}
