{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":421367,"duration_api_ms":421452,"num_turns":42,"result":"**Phase 4: AI 对接与流程打通** ✅ 主要功能已完成\n\n### 完成的功能：\n\n1. **数据库更新** (`src/lib/db/schema.ts`)\n   - 添加了 `aiTaskStatusEnum` 枚举\n   - AI 任务表使用状态枚举\n\n2. **API 接口**：\n   - `POST /api/products/[id]/submit` - 提交产品时自动创建 AI 任务\n   - `GET /api/ai/tasks?productId=xxx` - 客户端轮询任务状态\n   - `POST /api/ai/callback` - AI 服务回调，保存生成结果\n   - `POST /api/internal/ai/trigger` - 内部触发 AI 生成（包含模拟演示）\n   - `POST /api/admin/products/[id]/trigger-ai` - 管理员触发 AI\n\n3. **客户端轮询组件** (`src/components/task-status-poller.tsx`)\n   - 产品详情页自动轮询任务状态\n   - 状态变化时自动刷新页面\n\n4. **工作流程**：\n   - 客户提交产品 → 状态: submitted，创建 AI 任务 (pending)\n   - 管理员审核并触发 AI → 状态: queued → processing\n   - AI 生成完成回调 → 保存图片，状态: reviewing\n   - 客户端自动看到生成结果\n\n### 待完成：\n- 端到端流程测试（需要运行开发服务器实际测试）\n- Phase 5: 体验优化\n\n---\n\n项目构建成功，可运行 `npm run dev` 测试。","session_id":"0fe3e04a-e649-4c3b-ad04-3a2fa78bad13","total_cost_usd":1.5780760499999995,"usage":{"input_tokens":22350,"cache_creation_input_tokens":57540,"cache_read_input_tokens":1557720,"output_tokens":12172,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0}},"modelUsage":{"MiniMax-M2.5":{"inputTokens":24018,"outputTokens":16008,"cacheReadInputTokens":1558936,"cacheCreationInputTokens":212859,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.5780760499999995,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"bac91f99-75b0-4905-9a89-0744fc983545"}
